“Photography has been my passion since I started working at a photo lab in 2007. I used to develop all these wedding photographers’ films and think, “Wow, these are beautiful, I want to do this”. Fortunately, I did and loved it! Once I had completed my degree in Arts and Graphic design I decided to work independently. There has been no turning back since then.”
